FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Yes, we prioritize safety and hygiene. All sellers must follow our strict packaging and handling guidelines. We also have a rating system to ensure reliable transactions.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: What types of toilet paper can I trade on the platform?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: You can trade various types including standard rolls, jumbo rolls, recycled, scented, and even specialty toilet papers. Our marketplace accommodates all preferences and needs.
